          <p class="service-description">
            Alignment is the experience of living in harmony with yourself —
            when your emotions, body, and spirit are in conversation with one
            another, and your inner life is reflected in how you move through
            the world. When you are aligned, there is less force and more flow.
            You trust your internal guidance, allow emotions to move without
            resistance, and meet life with a sense of openness rather than
            control. From this place, clarity arises naturally, and your choices
            begin to feel rooted, authentic, and true to who you are. Alignment
            is not something to achieve — it is something to return to.
          </p>
        </div>

