          <h3 class="service-title">Embodiment</h3>
          <p class="service-description">
            Embodiment is the practice of allowing emotions to be felt fully,
            without suppression, avoidance, or numbing. Rather than seeing
            emotions as obstacles to healing or spirituality, embodiment honors
            them as essential messengers. When emotions are given space to
            surface and move, they bring clarity, release, and deeper
            self-trust. Through embodiment, we learn to live from within our
            bodies rather than over them — reconnecting with the wisdom that is
            already present and allowing our inner life to guide our outer
            expression.
          </p>
